I'm creating an assessment exercise for Module 7 of the DFIR-412 certification course (Phishing Detection and Analysis). This module addresses browser interface manipulation attacks, teaching candidates to recognize synthetic authentication screens, simulated browser chrome, and credential harvesting techniques in order to build enterprise detection workflows.

